orld is small, and a university is smaller. Being popular students at the same University leads Gun and Bar to collide with each other again and again.\\n\\nLOVE MECHANICS - A love story that starts one night in a club between an engineering major, Mark, who is absolutely drunk and carrying the painful burden of his one-sided love, and Wee who he bumps into and mistakes as the object of his affection, This is an imperfect love story between two imperfect human beings.\\n\\nTHIS IS LOVE - A love story about how the engineering faculty's resident playboy, Neur, secretly falls in love with Pra-Ram, a senior in high school and younger brother of Gun and how he wins the boy, and his brother over.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"100634","season":1,"vote_average":6.1,"vote_count":14},"modified":"2023-05-10T18:22:50.000Z","cast":["Atthanin Thaninphanuwiwat","Win Achawin Michaels","Folk Thitiphat Chankaew","Wanarat Ratsameerat","Anan Wong","Ratchapat Worrasarn","Wongrapee Krusong","Prat Itthichaicharoen","Saran Naksodsi","Thamrong Cunpisut","Supitcha Limsommut"],"director":["Niink Karnpicha Sinlertpattana","Ko Nantalit Tampacha"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Atthanin Thaninphanuwiwat","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Atthanin Thaninphanuwiwat","tmdb_id":2666135,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/d4HbkIfCNSOOXL9WYNkmbQIWUrx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2666135"},{"name":"Win Achawin Michaels","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Win Achawin Michaels","tmdb_id":2595476,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/htcyfeU7y5ezR949QRV0HG7z8Ec.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2595476"},{"name":"Folk Thitiphat Chankaew","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Folk Thitiphat Chankaew","tmdb_id":2595477,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6BspKqNyXfaL3jjwh3ckKsUT0T6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2595477"},{"name":"Wanarat Ratsameerat","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Wanarat Ratsameerat","tmdb_id":2595478,"profile":"https://image.tm